title: Tubelight Wrap Up Party: Salman Khan Spotted With Iulia & Rest Of The Crew
text: tweet Salman Khan has finally wrapped up the shooting of his next, Tubelight. A wrap party was held by the makers of the film to celebrate its completion. The entire crew and cast of the film including the film’s female lead, Chinese actress, Zhu Zhu were spotted at the party. Also, Salman’s rumored girlfriend, Iulia Vantur was seen in pictures with the star. Check out the video here: Tubelight Wrap-up Party Directed by Kabir Khan, the film is slated to release over Eid this year. SHARE
